  introLines:
  - You can't sue me! I don't even officially own those restaurants!
  - Hey, if you let me go to heaven, I can get you a lifetime supply of Nuggets.
    No questions asked
  answerWhatHappenedBefore: I heard sirens outside my office, grabbed my briefcase,
    sprinted down the back stairs, and took a devastating spill on some spilled grease.
  answerWhatKindOfLife: An efficient one. Why use real beef when soy filler saves
    you forty percent on production costs?
  answerWhatWasYourJob: I provided affordable, highly questionable meals to the masses.
    I built an empire on cheap ingredients.
  answerWhatHappenedClothes: Running a multi-million dollar bootleg burger empire
    is sticky business. This shirt is covered in corporate secrets.
  answerWhyHaveItem: It's a burger! It's perfectly safe! Well, mostly safe. I wouldn't
    recommend eating the bun if it's been glowing in the dark.
